```suggestion
try {
  registerDiagramIconPacks(config.icons);
} catch (error) {
  log.error('Failed to register icon packs, continuing with diagram render:', error);
}
```
If icon pack registration fails, it prevents the entire diagram from rendering. With the suggested change, this scenario can be avoided.

